title: Bobby’s Bronco Might Be Totaled + Amy’s Daughter Has an Awkward Airplane Injury + Bobby Reveals The Thing That Changed his life Because of His Wife

description:
Bobby JUST bought an old Bronco a few weeks ago…but he shares with us why it may be totaled now after someone wrecked into it. Amy shares a story from vacation where her daughter was hit in the eye with luggage by another passenger and it's just an awkward situation. Bobby is now a fan of…facials because of his wife. He reveals why they changed his life.
